-- Hungarian Life Insurer CIG Pannonia Declines to Lowest on Record
-- B y   A n d r a s   G e r g e l y
-- 2012-04-03T08:48:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-03/hungarian-life-insurer-cig-pannonia-declines-to-lowest-on-record.html
 CIG Pannonia Eletbiztosito Nyrt., a
Hungarian life insurer, slumped for a third day to a record low.  The shares dropped 2.2 percent to 406 forint by 10:38 a.m.
in Budapest, the lowest level since their November 2010 listing
and extending the decline in the past month to 21 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
